10.4.1.3 Paccayānulomapaccanīya
Mahantaraduka
Cittasampayuttaduka
Paṭiccavāra
Paccayānulomapaccanīya
152.
2689Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava…pe…  nakamme ekaṃ, navipāke pañca, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte ekaṃ, nonatthiyā tīṇi, novigate tīṇi.
